task.summary:
Issue with population being very similar as time progresses i.e. Random() does not get entirely random values resulting in the same indivduals being chosen over and over.
This causes identical individuals by generation 15, however all code indicates that it should be different
Fixed population issue, however optimal value remains the same from start.
